『All of the underground cities of Carvain have declined, and this deep

『Even if we escape from the poisonous breath of the dragon and develop
technology through magic, prosperity cannot continue without the
blessings of sunlight.

again for people?
『It's frustrating that I won't be able to witness it.

『The cave goblins are coming from the north, afraid of something.
